Package: betacal
Type: Package
Title: Beta Calibration
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Telmo de Menezes e Silva Filho
Maintainer: Telmo de Menezes e Silva Filho <tmfilho@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a beta_calibration function which 
    allows the user to fit any of our three proposed beta calibration 
    models, following "Kull, M., Silva Filho, T.M., Flach, P. Beta 
    calibration: a well-founded and easily implemented improvement on logistic 
    calibration for binary classifiers, AISTATS 2017 (in press)". The package 
    also provides a beta_predict function to obtaincalibrated probabilities
    from the fitted model.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
